
* 2011-08-25 - Sylvain Vedrenne <sylvain@jankenpoi.net>
  Version 0.7.1 - now the project supports ./configure && make && sudo make install
  as well as "make distcheck". Java + JNI + C code is used, compiled and made executable
  using a bash script containing the "java .... -jar XXX.jar" command. 
  After installation, a localized message from the C code is printed (the example is provide in French).

* 2011-08-22 - Sylvain Vedrenne
  Version 0.7 : the package is partially operational.

